歪頭菜葉微短稍硬又似穁芽葉頗長<graphic n="KR1359" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR1359.png" mimeType="image/png"/>其葉兩兩對<lb/>
